msgctxt "84_Chief Executive Officer"
msgid "There's some sort of a commotion over by the arena.\\r\n"
"What did I miss?"
msgstr "Parece que hay algún alboroto por la arena.\\r\n"
"¿Me perdí de algo?"

msgctxt "96_Chief Operating Officer"
msgid "Didn't you hear? The Florist just hosted an exhibition match\\r\n"
"between a new contender and the reigning champ."
msgstr "¿No te enteraste? El Florista montó un combate de exhibición\\r \n"
"entre un nuevo retador y el actual campeón."

msgctxt "108_Chief Executive Officer"
msgid "Oh, so that's why the casino emptied out..."
msgstr "Oh, entonces por eso no hay ni un alma en el casino..."

msgctxt "120_Chief Operating Officer"
msgid "It was the battle of the century! The challenger won,\\r\n"
"then struck a victory pose and gave an epic speech!"
msgstr "¡Pero que pelea más épica! ¡El retador salió victorioso,\\r\n"
"posó como todo un héroe y dió un discurso que puso la piel de gallina!"

msgctxt "132_Chief Operating Officer"
msgid "I've never seen anything like it in all my life!\\r\n"
"I sure wish you could've been there."
msgstr "¡En toda mi vida, nunca vi algo igual!\\r \n"
"Ojalá lo hubieras visto con tus propios ojos."

msgctxt "144_Chief Executive Officer"
msgid "You should've come to get me! I'm afraid this little lapse\\r\n"
"will reflect negatively on your annual assessment."
msgstr "¡Podrías haberme buscado!\\r \n"
"Me temo que este desliz te va a costar caro en tu evaluación anual."

msgctxt "156_Chief Operating Officer"
msgid "Hm..."
msgstr "Mm..."

